(689, 3, '2014-04-11 00:24:56', '2014-04-11 00:24:56', '', 'Overharvesting', 'OVERHARVESTING: Oysters are a delicious meal for both animals and humans alike, but when they are continuously harvested at a rate faster than they can reproduce, the natural population canât keep up, and their numbers begin to decline.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'threats3', '', '', '2014-04-11 00:24:56', '2014-04-11 00:24:56', '', 140, 'http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/threats31.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
