(1180, 5, '2014-11-06 20:34:19', '2014-11-06 20:34:19', '[gallery columns="5" link="file" ids="626,1053,54,622,1057"]\r\n\r\nMat-making workshops, hosted at various parks throughout Brevard County, are free and open to the public from 10:00 a.m. to 11:30 a.m., or until materials are depleted. All ages are welcome, materials will be provided for you, and no reservation is required. During the workshop, youâll be learning about our restoration projects and creating oyster mats by attaching oyster shells to squares of aquaculture mesh using zip ties. It usually takes between 15 and 20 minutes to make one oyster mat, and the oyster shells can be dusty, so try to wear clothing that you donât mind getting a bit dirty. Our public workshop schedule is as follows:\r\n\r\nNovember 1: <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Manatee+Sanctuary+Park/@28.394771,-80.618469,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x88e0a7ccddfd24a1:0xab50f5c92b9fa336" target="_blank">Manatee Sanctuary Park</a>\r\nNovember 5: <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Riverwalk:+A+Family+Park/@28.268128,-80.688734,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x88de038f372e150b:0x55bfd0a94052d255" target="_blank">Riverwalk Nature Cente</a>r\r\nNovember 12: <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Erna+Nixon+Park/@28.090212,-80.657237,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x88de0e6c8d80aab3:0x60351accbd927a4" target="_blank">Erna Nixon Park</a>\r\nNovember 19: <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Barrier+Island+Sanctuary/@27.902896,-80.47131,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x88de6a6c746b3f1f:0xc80600e189ec624b" target="_blank">Barrier Island Center</a>\r\nNovember 22: <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/David+R+Schechter+Community+Center/@28.183798,-80.60464,15z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0x14c18ce1be858833" target="_blank">David R Schechter Community Center</a>\r\n\r\nDecember 3: <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Riverwalk:+A+Family+Park/@28.268128,-80.688734,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x88de038f372e150b:0x55bfd0a94052