(1466, 5, '2015-12-31 20:46:30', '2015-12-31 20:46:30', '<strong>REFERENCE DOCUMENTS</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Web_CURRENT_Oyster-Gardening-Presentation.pdf" target="_blank">Oyster Gardening Presentation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/CURRENT_Brevard-Oyster-Gardening-Manual_Summer-2015_2.pdf" target="_blank">Brevard Oyster Gardening Manual</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>HABITAT DEPLOYMENT TIPS</strong>\r\n\r\n<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gMtef96P-lo" width="853" height="480" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<strong style="line-height: 1.5;">HABITAT MAINTENANCE TIPS</strong>\r\n\r\n<iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/0MoHFOpb3II" width="853" height="480" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<strong>OYSTER SPAT IDENTIFICATION GUIDES</strong>\r\n\r\nOyster spat 3 weeks post-distribution:\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" ids="740,739,737"]\r\n\r\nOyster spat time progression:\r\n\r\n[gallery columns="5" ids="1129,1130,1131,1132,1133"]\r\n\r\nOyster spat under fouling:\r\n\r\n[gallery columns="4" link="file" ids="843,844,845,849"]\r\n\r\n<strong>FOULING LEVEL DESIGNATION:</strong>\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" ids="743,1122,1125"]\r\n\r\n<strong>OYSTER COHABITANTS IDENTIFICATION GUIDES</strong>\r\n\r\nOyster friends:\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" columns="5" ids="773,727,820,1366,1367,1119,1120,1368,1369,1370"]\r\n\r\nOyster foes:\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" columns="5" ids="1375,721,772,1111,1112,1113,1115,1376,1377,1378"]\r\n\r\nFouling Organisms:\r\n\r\n[gallery columns="5" link="file" ids="770,728,726,768,771,1106,1380,1379,1384"]\r\n\r\nFound something in your habitat that you don''t see here? Look it up in the Smithsonian Marine Station''sÂ <a href="http://www.sms.si.edu/irlspec/SpeciesImageGallery.htm" target="_blank">Indian River Lagoon Species Database</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>DATA ENTRY TIPS:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Most fields in our database accept properly formatted numerals only, with the exception of "comment", "fouling load," and "other" fields.</li>\r\n	<li>Distances are assumed to be in feet, times are assumed to be in minutes, and weights are assumed to be in pounds, so do not type units of measure, or you will receive an error message.</li>\r\n	<li>Check box fields designate an affirmative answer if they are checked and a negative answer if they are not.</li>\r\n	<li>Dates are to be typed in the form dd/mm/yyyy, and phone numbers with area code are to be separated with periods instead of dashes.</li>\r\n	<li>The fields for Â yellow and green habitats are left over from a previous round of gardening and do not apply, so please leave them blank.</li>\r\n	<li>Please refer to the examples below...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>"Habitat Information" section:</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_1224" align="alignnone" width="1024"]<a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screen-Shot-2014-12-03-at-1.43.04-PM1.png"><img class=" wp-image-1224 " src="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screen-Shot-2014-12-03-at-1.43.04-PM1-1024x663.png" alt="Habitat Information" width="1024" height="663" /></a> This section records basic information about when and where you initially deployed your habitats. You will only need to fill it out once at the start of the program.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<strong>"Habitat Observations" section: </strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_1217" align="alignnone" width="1024"]<a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screen-Shot-2014-12-03-at-1.45.22-PM.png"><img class=" wp-image-1217   " src="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Screen-Shot-2014-12-03-at-1.45.22-PM-1024x711.png" alt="Habitat observations" width="1024" height="711" /></a> This section tracks changes to your habitats over time, such as growth of oysters and fouling, organisms present in your habitat, and the development of natural recruitment . You should enter data in this section each week as you perform your habitat maintenance.[/caption]', 'Oyster Gardening Resources', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '906-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-31 20:46:30', '2015-12-31 20:46:30', '', 906, 'http://brevardoystergardens.org/906-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
