(1114, 5, '2014-10-01 17:28:41', '2014-10-01 17:28:41', '<strong>REFERENCE DOCUMENTS</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Version2-_Oyster-Gardening-Presentation_2014.pdf">Oyster Gardening Presentation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Brevard-Oyster-Gardening-Manual_Version-2_2014.pdf">Brevard Oyster Gardening Manual</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n(For the above documents, please note that Gardeners who started the program before July 2014 have four habitats instead of two)\r\n\r\n<strong>HABITAT MAINTENANCE TIPS</strong>\r\n\r\n<iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/0MoHFOpb3II" height="480" width="853" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<strong>OYSTER SPAT IDENTIFICATION GUIDES</strong>\r\n\r\nOyster spat 3 weeks post-distribution:\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" ids="740,739,737"]\r\n\r\nOyster spat 5 weeks post-distribution:\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" ids="743,742"]\r\n\r\nOyster spat under fouling:\r\n\r\n[gallery columns="4" link="file" ids="843,844,845,849"]\r\n\r\n<strong>OYSTER COHABITANTS IDENTIFICATION GUIDES</strong>\r\n\r\nOyster friends:\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" ids="773,775,727,817,819,820"]\r\n\r\nOyster foes:\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" columns="5" ids="728,726,725,722,721,768,772,771,770,1106,1108,1111,1112,1113"]\r\n\r\nFound something in your habitat that you don''t see here? Look it up in the Smithsonian Marine Station''sÂ <a href="http://www.sms.si.edu/irlspec/SpeciesImageGallery.htm" target="_blank">Indian River Lagoon Species Database</a>.', 'Oyster Gardening Resources', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '906-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-01 17:28:41', '2014-10-01 17:28:41', '', 906, 'http://brevardoystergardens.org/906-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(983, 5, '2014-07-11 18:39:57', '2014-07-11 18:39:57', '<a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/home8.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-717" alt="home8" src="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/home8.jpg" width="706" height="625" /></a>\r\n\r\nOyster Gardening workshops are <b>only for qualified individuals</b> and require reservations in advance. If you are approved for a workshop, we will provide all necessary supplies, so just plan to arrive 15 minutes early for sign-in, then stay throughout the entirety of the two-and-a-half hour workshop. Â Oyster Gardening is a great activity to get the whole family involved with at home, but please note that gardening workshops are primarily directed toward adults.\r\n\r\n<b><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW DO I QUALIFY FOR A WORKSHOP?</span></b>\r\n\r\nOnly those who are qualified to be either an Oyster Gardener or Oyster Buddy may attend an Oyster Gardening workshop. The requirements for both designations are as follows:\r\n\r\n<b>Oyster Gardener</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Has a dock on the open Indian River Lagoon (not a canal) in Brevard County. Community docks for homeowners associations and condos can also be eligible, but check out these special <a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Community-Docks-Guidelines.docx">guidelines</a> first.</li>\r\n	<li>Can commit one to two hours of time per week to cleaning and monitoring oyster habitats and entering findings into a database</li>\r\n	<li>Not planning to be out of town for extended periods of time over the next six to seven months</li>\r\n	<li>Can lift 30 lbs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Oyster Buddy</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Able to temporarily fill in for traveling or sick Oyster Gardeners by committing one to two hours per week to maintaining and monitoring their habitats for them</li>\r\n	<li>Has access to a reliable means of transportation to Oyster Gardening sites</li>\r\n	<li>Can lift 30 lbs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Home9.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-718" alt="Home9" src="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Home9.jpg" width="707" height="643" /></a>\r\n\r\n<b>IF YOU MEET THE REQUIREMENTS</b> to be either an Oyster Gardener or Oyster Buddy, please <a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/?page_id=970">sign up </a>for an Oyster Gardening workshop. (Only one registration per family, please)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Oyster Gardening Workshops', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '903-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-11 18:39:57', '2014-07-11 18:39:57', '', 903, 'http://brevardoystergardens.org/?p=983', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
