ft 30 lbs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Home9.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-718" alt="Home9" src="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Home9.jpg" width="707" height="643" /></a>\r\n\r\n<b>IF YOU MEET THE REQUIREMENTS</b> to be either an Oyster Gardener or Oyster Buddy, please <a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/?page_id=970">sign up </a>for an Oyster Gardening workshop. (<em>Only one registration is necessary per family/group</em>).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Oyster Gardening Workshops', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '903-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-11 18:40:54', '2014-07-11 18:40:54', '', 903, 'http://brevardoystergardens.org/?p=984', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
