(1433, 5, '2015-10-09 18:59:48', '2015-10-09 18:59:48', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n(Please read through the requirements, then follow the link at the bottom of the page to sign up)\r\n\r\nOyster Gardening workshops are <b>only for qualified individuals</b> and require reservations in advance. If you are approved for a workshop, we will provide all necessary supplies, so just plan to arrive 15 minutes early for sign-in, then stay throughout the entirety of the two-hour workshop. Â Oyster Gardening is a great activity to get the whole family involved with at home, but please note that gardening workshops are primarily directed toward adults...\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone  wp-image-607" src="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Oysters_Kiwanis-Park-221-1024x676.jpg" alt="" width="740" height="486" />\r\n\r\n<b><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW DO I QUALIFY FOR A WORKSHOP?</span></b>\r\n\r\nOnly those who are qualified to be either an Oyster Gardener or Oyster Buddy may attend an Oyster Gardening workshop. The requirements for both designations are as follows:\r\n\r\n<b>Oyster Gardener</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Has a dock on the Â Indian River Lagoon in Brevard County. Community docks for homeowners associations and condos can also be eligible, but check out these special <a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Community-Docks-Guidelines.docx">guidelines</a> first.</li>\r\n	<li>Can commit one to two hours of time per week to cleaning and monitoring oyster habitats and entering findings into a database</li>\r\n	<li>Not planning to be out of town for extended periods of time (more than two weeks) over the next six to seven months</li>\r\n	<li>Can lift 30 lbs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Oyster Buddy</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Able to temporarily fill in for traveling or sick Oyster Gardeners by committing one to two hours per week to maintaining and monitoring their habitats for them</li>\r\n	<li>Has access to a reliable means of transportation to Oyster Gardening sites</li>\r\n	<li>Can lift 30 lbs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class="alignnone  wp-image-718" src="http://brevardoystergardens.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Home9.jpg" alt="Home9" width="707" height="643" />\r\n\r\n<b>IF YOU MEET THE REQUIREMENTS</b> to be either an Oyster Gardener or Oyster Buddy, please visit our <a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/volunteer/" target="_blank">Volunteer</a><a href="http://brevardoystergardens.org/get-involved/">Â </a>page to sign upÂ for an upcoming oyster gardening workshop. <em>Only one registration is necessary per family/group.Â </em>', 'Oyster Gardening Workshops', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '903-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-09 18:59:48', '2015-10-09 18:59:48', '', 903, 'http://brevardoystergardens.org/903-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
